CatDescriptText: George M. Leader was governor of Pennsylvania from 1955-1959.  David L. Lawrence was governor of Pennsylvania from 1959-1963.  He died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Women, including Katharyne Anne Irvis in back seat of campaign car for David L. Lawrence for Governor, George M. Leader for Senator, and K. Leroy Irvis and Jason Clark for State Legislature
